race.comment: DASHING JORDY (5) looks close to another win after finishing third last time (30.89) at this track. Form here at this distance is sound. Boasts a strong record from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Top prospect. WHITE HAWKE (1) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a half a length second (30.85) over 530m at this track and making it two placings on end. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from four attempts. Deserves a win and gets his chance. HOUSE OF WONG (2) was game in defeat off a low draw at the latest outing, finishing second and beaten 1.75 lengths (30.84) behind ADHANA MARTINA at this track. Expected to feature. AGENT TWENTY ONE (3) has ability and can find the frame.
